<p>The usual format is that each author will have the opportunity to express their opinion on a topic of clinical or
  public health importance within 750 words, 10 references maximum, and one display item. Each piece will then be sent
  to the other participant who will be allowed 300 words to respond. Authors should aim to produce a constructive
  criticism of their opponent's views.</p>

<p>In some cases, we will commission a series of at least three different viewpoints on a topic. In this case, we do not
